flowchart TD
    A[Retrieval API request] --> B[Validate project_id and request]
    B --> C{Retrieval mode}

    C -->|vector| V1[Embed query]
    V1 --> V2[pgvector search chunks]
    V2 --> V3[Filter by project_id]
    V3 --> V4[Return vector candidates]

    C -->|keyword| K1[Build text search query]
    K1 --> K2[PostgreSQL full-text search]
    K2 --> K3[Filter by project_id]
    K3 --> K4[Return keyword candidates]

    C -->|hybrid| H1[Embed query]
    H1 --> H2[Fetch vector candidates]
    C --> H3[Fetch keyword candidates]
    H2 --> H4[Merge by chunk_id]
    H3 --> H4
    H4 --> H5[Normalize scores]
    H5 --> H6[Apply weighted fusion]
    H6 --> H7[Sort and trim top_k]

    V4 --> R[Build retrieval response]
    K4 --> R
    H7 --> R

    R --> L1[Create retrieval_log]
    L1 --> L2[Create retrieval_log_chunks]
    L2 --> API[Return results with scores and retrieval_log_id]

    subgraph Isolation[Required Isolation]
        P[Every chunk query includes project_id]
    end

    V3 -. enforced .-> P
    K3 -. enforced .-> P
    H4 -. merged candidates retain project_id .-> P
